===Noun===
'''die Straße''' (''pl:'' [[Straßen]])



# a paved [[road]], especially in the city. [[Street]], [[road]] ''Die Straße ist [[breit]].'' (The street is wide.)
# the part of the [[road]] on which one drives, as opposed to the [[boardwalk]]. ''Das Kind überquerte die Straße'' (The child crossed the road)
